    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Glide是一款实验性的快节奏街机游戏，仅支持惯性鼠标控制（但你也可以使用游戏手柄或鼠标+WASD）。在神秘主机的指令下，一个小而脆弱的机器人在奇异的机械世界中苏醒，必须克服越来越困难的关卡，这些关卡充满了各种敌对机器人和危险障碍，并完成其主要目标。这就是它的程序所说的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏操作有点特殊，但还是很简单的：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动鼠标以控制角色的移动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按住鼠标左键射击并在与移动方向无关的一个方向上固定瞄准</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在射击过程中，您可以通过按鼠标右键将瞄准快速旋转180度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动物体（钥匙）和在交通站移动平台也是通过按住鼠标左键完成的</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您需要提示，其中包含级别目标，只需单击鼠标中键（滚轮）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在创作这个游戏时，我受到过去的抗战游戏的启发，试图逼近同样充满亢奋的游戏体验，但添加了现代图形和效果。这个游戏面向那些喜欢技巧和技能动作游戏的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
